data.description: Assumable 2.25% loan available to qualified buyer. Beautiful custom brick ranch home situated on over 5 acres in Oxford Township. Home features cathedral living room with fireplace, 9ft ceilings throughout, 4 bedrooms and 3-1 bathrooms with deluxe primary bedroom that walks out to beautiful in-ground pool. Brazilian cherry floors, large eat-in kitchen, formal dining room and walk-in closets in all bedrooms. Large 3 car garage and partially finished lower level.
